  "description": "<p>From dawn patrols to first ascents, the Shadow hoodie keeps you reliably warm during your winter adventures. Insulated with VerticalX ECO SR, a sustainable alternative to down, it provides warmth and loft with less impact on the planet. The face fabric is wind- and water-resistant for protection on days when you don't want a shell, great for comfort on or off the mountain.</p><ul><li>Stretch woven nylon shell and lining moves with you and resists abrasion</li><li>Vertical ECO SR\u2122 insulation has loft without bulk, like down, but maintains warmth when wet</li><li>Insulation is made with Repreve\u00ae recycled polyester and Soronoa\u00ae plant-based fabric</li><li>Zippered handwarmer pockets provide some protection when you're not wearing gloves</li><li>Elastic cuffs with thumb loops, and an adjustable drawcord hem seal out drafts</li></ul>",
